<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p>You are well prepared. 你们准备得很充分。</p>
<p>That’s great team work.团队合作出色。</p>
<p>You have been a wonderful leader.你的领导能力很棒。</p>
<p>Your organization was great.你组织得很出色。</p>
<p>对学生课堂表现的赞赏：</p>
<p>Well put! 表达得很好。</p>
<p>That’s exactly the point.说到点子上了。</p>
<p>I couldn’t have given a better answer myself.我自己都想不出更好的答案。</p>
<p>I was so impressed by your performance.你的表现让我印象深刻。</p>
<p>It was a neat presentation.展示得干脆利索。</p>
<p>I appreciate your idea/handwriting/efforts/diligence.我欣赏你的想法/书写/努力/勤奋。</p>
<p>That’s a very good observation.评论得非常好。</p>
<p>学生表现不尽如人意时的安慰： A good try. / A nice attempt.不错的尝试。</p>
<p>On the whole, it is very good.总的来说非常好。</p>
<p>You are doing fine.你做得不错。</p>
<p>I believe you can do better next time.我相信你下次会做得更好。</p>
<p>You were nearly right.你差一点点就答对了。</p>
<p>You are on the right track.你的思路没错。</p>
